Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.main.utils.tests

Class Test

java.lang.Object
org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.main.utils.tests.Test
Direct Known Subclasses:
IntegrationTest, UnitTest
public abstract class Test extends Object

A Test is a piece of code that can be ran to test other code. Tests will be ran automatically by the Tester unless they have an @Skippable annotation.

Tests should be able to be fully autonomous. A Test's environment should be fully controlled by the Test. Tests should set up their environments in their constructor.
